price: Oyruun sun lamaanuu firii isii odoo homaa isarraa hin hirdhisin kennite; gidduu isaaniitii laga maddisiifne (san fakkeenya godhiif)
arabic: كِلۡتَا ٱلۡجَنَّتَيۡنِ ءَاتَتۡ أُكُلَهَا وَلَمۡ تَظۡلِم مِّنۡهُ شَيۡـٔٗاۚ وَفَجَّرۡنَا خِلَٰلَهُمَا نَهَرٗا

version.title: Oromo translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Oromo by Ghaly Ababour Abaghuna, printed in 2009.

meta.transliteration: kil'tā al-janatayni ātat ukulahā walam taẓlim min'hu shayan wafajjarnā khilālahumā naharan
translations: And We caused to gush forth
